<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF109-585-533  </DOCNO><DOCID>09 585 533.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>Newsbytes  Nov 6 1990* Full Text COPYRIGHT Newsbytes Inc. 1990.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>N.Y. State police nab brothers in harassment case. (DanielRosenbaum and brother arrested )</TITLE><AUTHOR>McMullen, Barbara E.; McMullen, John F.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   IDG Development Corp. (Investigations).andO;Topic:     Computer CrimesLaw EnforcementTelephone CompaniesLegal Issues.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>NY STATE POLICE NAB BROTHERS IN HARASSMENT CASE 11/06/90 NEW YORK, NEW YORK,U.S.A., 1990 NOV 6 (NB) -- The New York State Police, working in concert withSecret Service investigators, have arrested Daniel Rosenbaum, age 17, and hisfourteen year old brother for allegedy harassing IDG Corporation by telephoneresulting in revenue losses to IDG of an estimated $2.4 million.andM;New York State Police Special Investigator Donald Delaney told Newsbytes:&quot;The Rosenbaums have made over 700 telephone calls to IDG since July of thisyear.andP;  They have tampered with voice mail boxes, erased advertising materialfrom clients, entered bomb threats, and disrupted the IDG voice telephonesystem.andP;  They admitted making the calls to annoy and to take over IDG's voicemail system.andP;  The calls were supposedly made because of a grievance DanielRosenbaum had against IDG.andP;  According to Rosenbaum, he subscribed to an IDGmagazine and did not receive a free poster due him with the subscription.andP;  Hecontacted IDG twice and upon receiving no satisfaction, began the harassmentcampaign.&quot;andM;The Rosenbaums have been charged with computer tampering, aggravatedharassment, and unauthorized use of a computer.andP;  The younger Rosenbaum isbeing charged as a minor.andP;  While these charges are misdemeanors, Delaney toldNewsbytes: &quot;We are anticipating additional charges including felonies.&quot;andM;The State Police also seized a memory telephone system which was allegedlythe single instrument used in the harassment.andP;  According to Delaney, thetelephone had IDG's toll free number encoded and IDG's name written on theoutside of the unit.andM;(Barbara E. McMullen andamp; John F. McMullen/19901106/0930PST)</TEXT></DOC>